<P><FONT SIZE='3'><B><U>Intrusion Detection System</U></B></FONT></P>

<P>This page is used to activate/deactivate the IDS (Intrustion Detection
System) mechanism. To <B>Enable</B>, tick the box and click save, to
disable untick the box and click <B>Save</B>. Logs are available from the
IDS logviewer in real time, which is accessed from the <B>Logs</B> page.</P>
